<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SSU - Social Service Unit</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style1.css" />
  <!-- Add Font Awesome -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    .header-right {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-left: 2rem;
    }

    .icon-button {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 50%;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .icon-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      background: #f8f8f8;
    }

    .icon-button[data-tooltip]:before {
      content: attr(data-tooltip);
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -35px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: #333;
      color: white;
      font-size: 12px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .icon-button[data-tooltip]:hover:before {
      opacity: 1;
      visibility: visible;
    }

    .logout-btn {
      color: #e74c3c;
    }

    .logout-btn:hover {
      background: #fff0f0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .header-right {
        margin-left: 1rem;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }
      
      .icon-button {
        width: 35px;
        height: 35px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <% if (locals.user) { %>
    <div class="welcome-popup">
      <span class="welcome-title">✨ Welcome to SSU ✨</span>
      <span class="welcome-name"><%= user.name %></span>
      <span class="welcome-tagline">Together we make a difference!</span>
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <header class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">SSU <span>Social Service Unit</span></div>
    <nav>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about1">About us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/userevents">Event</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contact us</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <div class="header-right">
      <a href="/profile" class="icon-button" data-tooltip="My Profile">
        <i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i>
      </a>
      <a href="/logout" class="icon-button logout-btn" data-tooltip="Sign Out">
        <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>How can social services agencies become more agile?</h1>
      <div class="hero-slider">
        <div class="slider-track">
          <div class="slide">
            <img src="/image/cleaning.png" alt="Cleaning Campaign">
            <div class="slide-label">
              <span class="label-text">Community Cleaning</span>
              <span class="label-description">Making our world cleaner, one step at a time</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="slide">
            <img src="/image/Volunter.png" alt="Volunteer Work">
            <div class="slide-label">
              <span class="label-text">Volunteer Work</span>
              <span class="label-description">Together we can make a difference</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="slide">
            <img src="/image/awarness.png" alt="Awareness Programs">
            <div class="slide-label">
              <span class="label-text">Awareness Programs</span>
              <span class="label-description">Educating for a better tomorrow</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slider-nav">
          <span class="dot active"></span>
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span class="dot"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services">
    <h2>We Always Provide The Best Service</h2>
    <div class="description">
      <p>Services</p>
      <p>We provide help to those in need by organizing cleaning campaigns in neighborhoods, conducting volunteer drives, and raising awareness through outreach programs. Our aim is to build a healthier and more connected community.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-cards">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/image/cleaning.png" alt="Cleaning Campaign" />
        <h3>Cleaning Campaign</h3>
        <p>We organize neighborhood clean-up drives, ensuring the spaces where we live and play are clean and safe for everyone.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/image/Volunter.png" alt="Volunteer Work" />
        <h3>Volunteer Work</h3>
        <p>Our volunteers actively participate in helping the elderly, tutoring children, and supporting local events that need manpower.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/image/awarness.png" alt="Awareness Program" />
        <h3>Awareness and Outreach Programs</h3>
        <p>From health to education, we run various campaigns to keep the public informed and involved in improving community wellbeing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact">
    <h2>Find us</h2>
    <ul class="contact-list">
      <li><strong>Call Us</strong><br /><a href="tel:+123456789">+123 456 789</a></li>
      <li><strong>Email Now</strong><br /><a href="mailto:ssu@agency.org">ssu@agency.org</a></li>
      <li><strong>Location</strong><br />Street 123, New York, USA</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="company-info">
        <h3>Know More</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">Support</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Terms & Conditions</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="newsletter">
        <h3>Newsletter</h3>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" />
        <button>Send</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Social Service Unit. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
